{"title":"CSS语法初探以及使用","uid":"06cb31f739141f028e7d96fc342e06c9","slug":"CSS语法初探以及使用","date":"2022-03-30T02:44:00.000Z","updated":"2022-04-04T13:25:49.396Z","comments":true,"path":"api/articles/CSS语法初探以及使用.json","keywords":"C++,Pyhton,Java,算法","cover":"img/css.jpeg","content":"<h2 id=\"css语法\"><a class=\"markdownIt-Anchor\" href=\"#css语法\"></a> CSS语法</h2>\n<p>CSS规则由两个主要的部分构成：选择器，以及一条或多条声明</p>\n<p>选择器通常是您需要改变样式的对象，这些对象可以是某个标签、所有网页对象、指定Class或ID值等。<br />\n每条声明由一个属性和一个值组成。<br />\n属性是CSS提供的设置好的样式选项。每个属性有一个值。属性和值被冒号分隔开。<br />\n属性值是用来显示属性效果的参数。它包括数值和单位，或者关键字。<br />\nCSS声明总是以分号 ; 结束，声明总以大括号 {} 括起来</p>\n<p>例如：</p>\n<pre class=\"line-numbers language-css\" data-language=\"css\"><code class=\"language-css\"><span class=\"token selector\">body</span>\n<span class=\"token punctuation\">&#123;</span>\n  <span class=\"token property\">front-size</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">:</span> 12px<span class=\"token punctuation\">;</span>\n  <span class=\"token property\">color</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">:</span> #333<span class=\"token punctuation\">;</span>\n<span class=\"token punctuation\">&#125;</span><span aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"line-numbers-rows\"><span></span><span></span><span></span><span></span><span></span></span></code></pre>\n<p>在这个例子中，body就是选择器，表示&lt;body&gt;这个标签。</p>\n<p>front-size:12px;和color:#333;就是该条CSS的两个声明。</p>\n<p>在声明中，冒号前面的是属性，后面的是属性值。</p>\n<p>一般在属性值和前面的冒号之间放一个空格，会更加美观。字母最好全部小写。</p>\n<h2 id=\"css应用\"><a class=\"markdownIt-Anchor\" href=\"#css应用\"></a> CSS应用</h2>\n<p>CSS样式代码必须保存在.css文件中(链接式、导入式)，或者放在网页内style标签中(内嵌式)，或者插在网页标签的style属性值中(行内样式)。</p>\n<h3 id=\"行内样式\"><a class=\"markdownIt-Anchor\" href=\"#行内样式\"></a> 行内样式：</h3>\n<pre class=\"line-numbers language-html\" data-language=\"html\"><code class=\"language-html\"><span class=\"token doctype\"><span class=\"token punctuation\">&lt;!</span><span class=\"token doctype-tag\">doctype</span> <span class=\"token name\">html</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">></span></span>\n<span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token punctuation\">&lt;</span>html</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">></span></span>\n\n<span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token punctuation\">&lt;</span>head</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">></span></span>\n    <span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token punctuation\">&lt;</span>meta</span> <span class=\"token attr-name\">charset</span><span class=\"token attr-value\"><span class=\"token punctuation attr-equals\">=</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">\"</span>utf-8<span class=\"token punctuation\">\"</span></span><span class=\"token punctuation\">></span></span>\n    <span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token punctuation\">&lt;</span>title</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">></span></span><span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token punctuation\">&lt;/</span>title</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">></span></span>\n<span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token punctuation\">&lt;/</span>head</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">></span></span>\n\n<span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token punctuation\">&lt;</span>body</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">></span></span>\n    <span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token punctuation\">&lt;</span>p</span> <span class=\"token special-attr\"><span class=\"token attr-name\">style</span><span class=\"token attr-value\"><span class=\"token punctuation attr-equals\">=</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">\"</span><span class=\"token value css language-css\"><span class=\"token property\">background-color</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">:</span> #999900</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">\"</span></span></span><span class=\"token punctuation\">></span></span>行内元素，控制段落-1<span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token punctuation\">&lt;/</span>p</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">></span></span>\n    <span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token punctuation\">&lt;</span>h2</span> <span class=\"token special-attr\"><span class=\"token attr-name\">style</span><span class=\"token attr-value\"><span class=\"token punctuation attr-equals\">=</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">\"</span><span class=\"token value css language-css\"><span class=\"token property\">background-color</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">:</span> #FF6633</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">\"</span></span></span><span class=\"token punctuation\">></span></span>行内元素，h2标题元素<span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token punctuation\">&lt;/</span>h2</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">></span></span>\n    <span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token punctuation\">&lt;</span>p</span> <span class=\"token special-attr\"><span class=\"token attr-name\">style</span><span class=\"token attr-value\"><span class=\"token punctuation attr-equals\">=</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">\"</span><span class=\"token value css language-css\"><span class=\"token property\">background-color</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">:</span> #999900</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">\"</span></span></span><span class=\"token punctuation\">></span></span>行内元素，控制段落-2<span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token punctuation\">&lt;/</span>p</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">></span></span>\n    <span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token punctuation\">&lt;</span>strong</span> <span class=\"token special-attr\"><span class=\"token attr-name\">style</span><span class=\"token attr-value\"><span class=\"token punctuation attr-equals\">=</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">\"</span><span class=\"token value css language-css\"><span class=\"token property\">font-size</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">:</span> 30px<span class=\"token punctuation\">;</span></span><span class=\"token punctuation\">\"</span></span></span><span class=\"token punctuation\">></span></span>行内元素，strong比em效果要强<span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token punctuation\">&lt;/</span>strong</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">></span></span>\n    <span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token punctuation\">&lt;</span>div</span> <span class=\"token special-attr\"><span class=\"token attr-name\">style</span><span class=\"token attr-value\"><span class=\"token punctuation attr-equals\">=</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">\"</span><span class=\"token value css language-css\"><span class=\"token property\">background-color</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">:</span> #66CC99<span class=\"token punctuation\">;</span> <span class=\"token property\">color</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">:</span> #993300<span class=\"token punctuation\">;</span><span class=\"token property\">height</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">:</span> 30px<span class=\"token punctuation\">;</span> <span class=\"token property\">line-height</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">:</span> 30px<span class=\"token punctuation\">;</span></span><span class=\"token punctuation\">\"</span></span></span><span class=\"token punctuation\">></span></span>行内元素，div块级元素<span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token punctuation\">&lt;/</span>div</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">></span></span>\n    <span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token punctuation\">&lt;</span>em</span> <span class=\"token special-attr\"><span class=\"token attr-name\">style</span><span class=\"token attr-value\"><span class=\"token punctuation attr-equals\">=</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">\"</span><span class=\"token value css language-css\"><span class=\"token property\">font-size</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">:</span> 2em<span class=\"token punctuation\">;</span></span><span class=\"token punctuation\">\"</span></span></span><span class=\"token punctuation\">></span></span>行内元素，em强调<span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token punctuation\">&lt;/</span>em</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">></span></span>\n<span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token punctuation\">&lt;/</span>body</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">></span></span>\n\n<span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token punctuation\">&lt;/</span>html</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">></span></span><span aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"line-numbers-rows\"><span></span><span></span><span></span><span></span><span></span><span></span><span></span><span></span><span></span><span></span><span></span><span></span><span></span><span></span><span></span><span></span><span></span><span></span></span></code></pre>\n<p>直接将CSS的声明作为style的属性值。多个声明之间用分号间隔。只能操作当前一个元素，优先级最高。</p>\n<h3 id=\"内嵌式\"><a class=\"markdownIt-Anchor\" href=\"#内嵌式\"></a> 内嵌式</h3>\n<pre class=\"line-numbers language-html\" data-language=\"html\"><code class=\"language-html\"><span class=\"token doctype\"><span class=\"token punctuation\">&lt;!</span><span class=\"token doctype-tag\">doctype</span> <span class=\"token name\">html</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">></span></span>\n<span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token punctuation\">&lt;</span>html</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">></span></span>\n\n<span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token punctuation\">&lt;</span>head</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">></span></span>\n    <span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token punctuation\">&lt;</span>meta</span> <span class=\"token attr-name\">charset</span><span class=\"token attr-value\"><span class=\"token punctuation attr-equals\">=</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">\"</span>utf-8<span class=\"token punctuation\">\"</span></span><span class=\"token punctuation\">></span></span>\n    <span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token punctuation\">&lt;</span>title</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">></span></span><span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token punctuation\">&lt;/</span>title</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">></span></span>\n    <span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token punctuation\">&lt;</span>style</span> <span class=\"token attr-name\">type</span><span class=\"token attr-value\"><span class=\"token punctuation attr-equals\">=</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">\"</span>text/css<span class=\"token punctuation\">\"</span></span><span class=\"token punctuation\">></span></span><span class=\"token style\"><span class=\"token language-css\">\n        <span class=\"token selector\">p</span> <span class=\"token punctuation\">&#123;</span>\n            <span class=\"token property\">text-align</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">:</span> left<span class=\"token punctuation\">;</span>\n            <span class=\"token comment\">/* 文本左对齐 */</span>\n            <span class=\"token property\">font-size</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">:</span> 18px<span class=\"token punctuation\">;</span>\n            <span class=\"token comment\">/* 字体大小18像素 */</span>\n            <span class=\"token property\">line-height</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">:</span> 25px<span class=\"token punctuation\">;</span>\n            <span class=\"token comment\">/* 行高25像素 */</span>\n            <span class=\"token property\">width</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">:</span> 500px<span class=\"token punctuation\">;</span>\n            <span class=\"token comment\">/* 段落宽度500像素 */</span>\n            <span class=\"token property\">margin</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">:</span> 0 auto<span class=\"token punctuation\">;</span>\n            <span class=\"token comment\">/* 浏览器下居中 */</span>\n            <span class=\"token property\">margin-bottom</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">:</span> 20px<span class=\"token punctuation\">;</span>\n            <span class=\"token comment\">/* 段落下边距20像素 */</span>\n        <span class=\"token punctuation\">&#125;</span>\n    </span></span><span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token punctuation\">&lt;/</span>style</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">></span></span>\n<span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token punctuation\">&lt;/</span>head</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">></span></span>\n\n<span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token punctuation\">&lt;</span>body</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">></span></span>\n    <span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token punctuation\">&lt;</span>p</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">></span></span>某个地方有个正在旅行的魔女，<span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token punctuation\">&lt;</span>br</span> <span class=\"token punctuation\">/></span></span>她的名字是伊蕾娜。<span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token punctuation\">&lt;</span>br</span> <span class=\"token punctuation\">/></span></span>身为旅人，<span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token punctuation\">&lt;</span>br</span> <span class=\"token punctuation\">/></span></span>在很长很长的旅途中，<span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token punctuation\">&lt;</span>br</span> <span class=\"token punctuation\">/></span></span>她与形形色色的国家与人们邂逅。<span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token punctuation\">&lt;/</span>p</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">></span></span>\n    <span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token punctuation\">&lt;</span>p</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">></span></span>只允许魔法师入境的国家、<span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token punctuation\">&lt;</span>br</span> <span class=\"token punctuation\">/></span></span>最喜欢肌肉的壮汉、<span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token punctuation\">&lt;</span>br</span> <span class=\"token punctuation\">/></span></span>在死亡深渊等待恋人归来的青年、<span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token punctuation\">&lt;</span>br</span> <span class=\"token punctuation\">/></span></span>独自留守国家早已灭亡的公主…<span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token punctuation\">&lt;/</span>p</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">></span></span>\n    <span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token punctuation\">&lt;</span>p</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">></span></span>最后，还有她身为魔女的至今为止与从今以后。<span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token punctuation\">&lt;</span>br</span> <span class=\"token punctuation\">/></span></span>和莫名其妙、滑稽可笑的人们相遇，<span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token punctuation\">&lt;</span>br</span> <span class=\"token punctuation\">/></span></span>接触某人美丽的日常生活，<span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token punctuation\">&lt;</span>br</span> <span class=\"token punctuation\">/></span></span>魔女日复一日编织出相逢与离别的故事。<span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token punctuation\">&lt;/</span>p</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">></span></span>\n<span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token punctuation\">&lt;/</span>body</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">></span></span>\n\n<span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token punctuation\">&lt;/</span>html</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">></span></span><span aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"line-numbers-rows\"><span></span><span></span><span></span><span></span><span></span><span></span><span></span><span></span><span></span><span></span><span></span><span></span><span></span><span></span><span></span><span></span><span></span><span></span><span></span><span></span><span></span><span></span><span></span><span></span><span></span><span></span><span></span><span></span><span></span><span></span><span></span></span></code></pre>\n<p>将CSS的内容直接写入网页源文件的&lt;style&gt;标签内部，只能控制当前一个页面，一般情况下&lt;style&gt;标签位于&lt;head&gt;内，但实际上&lt;style&gt;标签也可放在其他地方。</p>\n<p>注意，&lt;style&gt;不仅可以定义CSS样式，还可以定义JavaScript脚本。常用属性为type(类型)、title(样式名称)。<br />\n其中，type的属性值有text/css和test/javascript。</p>\n<p>一个网页可以有多个CSS样式表，一个网页文档中有多个&lt;style&gt;标签，就有多个样式表。通过title属性可以做到在多种样式直接切换。</p>\n<p>例如：</p>\n<pre class=\"line-numbers language-html\" data-language=\"html\"><code class=\"language-html\"><span class=\"token doctype\"><span class=\"token punctuation\">&lt;!</span><span class=\"token doctype-tag\">doctype</span> <span class=\"token name\">html</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">></span></span>\n<span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token punctuation\">&lt;</span>html</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">></span></span>\n\n<span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token punctuation\">&lt;</span>head</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">></span></span>\n    <span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token punctuation\">&lt;</span>meta</span> <span class=\"token attr-name\">charset</span><span class=\"token attr-value\"><span class=\"token punctuation attr-equals\">=</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">\"</span>utf-8<span class=\"token punctuation\">\"</span></span><span class=\"token punctuation\">></span></span>\n    <span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token punctuation\">&lt;</span>title</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">></span></span><span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token punctuation\">&lt;/</span>title</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">></span></span>\n    <span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token punctuation\">&lt;</span>style</span> <span class=\"token attr-name\">type</span><span class=\"token attr-value\"><span class=\"token punctuation attr-equals\">=</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">\"</span>text/css<span class=\"token punctuation\">\"</span></span> <span class=\"token attr-name\">title</span><span class=\"token attr-value\"><span class=\"token punctuation attr-equals\">=</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">\"</span>字体14号<span class=\"token punctuation\">\"</span></span><span class=\"token punctuation\">></span></span><span class=\"token style\"><span class=\"token language-css\">\n        <span class=\"token selector\">p</span> <span class=\"token punctuation\">&#123;</span>\n            <span class=\"token property\">text-align</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">:</span> left<span class=\"token punctuation\">;</span>\n            <span class=\"token comment\">/* 文本左对齐 */</span>\n            <span class=\"token property\">font-size</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">:</span> 14px<span class=\"token punctuation\">;</span>\n            <span class=\"token comment\">/* 字体大小14像素 */</span>\n            <span class=\"token property\">line-height</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">:</span> 25px<span class=\"token punctuation\">;</span>\n            <span class=\"token comment\">/* 行高25像素 */</span>\n            <span class=\"token property\">width</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">:</span> 500px<span class=\"token punctuation\">;</span>\n            <span class=\"token comment\">/* 段落宽度500像素 */</span>\n            <span class=\"token property\">margin</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">:</span> 0 auto<span class=\"token punctuation\">;</span>\n            <span class=\"token comment\">/* 浏览器下居中 */</span>\n        <span class=\"token punctuation\">&#125;</span>\n    </span></span><span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token punctuation\">&lt;/</span>style</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">></span></span>\n    <span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token punctuation\">&lt;</span>style</span> <span class=\"token attr-name\">type</span><span class=\"token attr-value\"><span class=\"token punctuation attr-equals\">=</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">\"</span>text/css<span class=\"token punctuation\">\"</span></span> <span class=\"token attr-name\">title</span><span class=\"token attr-value\"><span class=\"token punctuation attr-equals\">=</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">\"</span>字体18号<span class=\"token punctuation\">\"</span></span><span class=\"token punctuation\">></span></span><span class=\"token style\"><span class=\"token language-css\">\n        <span class=\"token selector\">p</span> <span class=\"token punctuation\">&#123;</span>\n            <span class=\"token property\">text-align</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">:</span> left<span class=\"token punctuation\">;</span>\n            <span class=\"token comment\">/* 文本左对齐 */</span>\n            <span class=\"token property\">font-size</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">:</span> 18px<span class=\"token punctuation\">;</span>\n            <span class=\"token comment\">/* 字体大小18像素 */</span>\n            <span class=\"token property\">line-height</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">:</span> 25px<span class=\"token punctuation\">;</span>\n            <span class=\"token comment\">/* 行高25像素 */</span>\n            <span class=\"token property\">width</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">:</span> 500px<span class=\"token punctuation\">;</span>\n            <span class=\"token comment\">/* 段落宽度500像素 */</span>\n            <span class=\"token property\">margin</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">:</span> 0 auto<span class=\"token punctuation\">;</span>\n            <span class=\"token comment\">/* 浏览器下居中 */</span>\n        <span class=\"token punctuation\">&#125;</span>\n\n        <span class=\"token selector\">p</span> <span class=\"token punctuation\">&#123;</span>\n            <span class=\"token property\">color</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">:</span> #6699FF<span class=\"token punctuation\">;</span>\n            <span class=\"token comment\">/* 字体颜色的改变 */</span>\n        <span class=\"token punctuation\">&#125;</span>\n    </span></span><span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token punctuation\">&lt;/</span>style</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">></span></span>\n<span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token punctuation\">&lt;/</span>head</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">></span></span>\n\n<span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token punctuation\">&lt;</span>body</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">></span></span>\n    <span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token punctuation\">&lt;</span>p</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">></span></span>精灵，存在于邻界，被指定为特殊灾害的生命体。<span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token punctuation\">&lt;</span>br</span> <span class=\"token punctuation\">/></span></span>（精霊、隣界に存在する特殊災害指定生命体。）<span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token punctuation\">&lt;</span>br</span> <span class=\"token punctuation\">/></span></span>\n        处置方法1，以武力歼灭精灵。<span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token punctuation\">&lt;</span>br</span> <span class=\"token punctuation\">/></span></span>（対処法１、武力を以てこれを殲滅する。）<span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token punctuation\">&lt;</span>br</span> <span class=\"token punctuation\">/></span></span>\n        处置方法2，与精灵约会，使其娇羞。<span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token punctuation\">&lt;</span>br</span> <span class=\"token punctuation\">/></span></span>（対処法２、デートして、デレさせる。） ”\n    <span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token punctuation\">&lt;/</span>p</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">></span></span>\n<span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token punctuation\">&lt;/</span>body</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">></span></span>\n\n<span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token punctuation\">&lt;/</span>html</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">></span></span><span aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"line-numbers-rows\"><span></span><span></span><span></span><span></span><span></span><span></span><span></span><span></span><span></span><span></span><span></span><span></span><span></span><span></span><span></span><span></span><span></span><span></span><span></span><span></span><span></span><span></span><span></span><span></span><span></span><span></span><span></span><span></span><span></span><span></span><span></span><span></span><span></span><span></span><span></span><span></span><span></span><span></span><span></span><span></span><span></span><span></span><span></span><span></span><span></span><span></span><span></span><span></span><span></span></span></code></pre>\n<h3 id=\"链接式\"><a class=\"markdownIt-Anchor\" href=\"#链接式\"></a> 链接式：</h3>\n<p>链接式就是通过&lt;link /&gt;标签将外部样式表文件链接到HTML文档中。这是网络上网站应用最多的方式，同时也是最实用的方式。增强网页结构的拓展性和CSS样式的可维护性。<br />\n<strong>例如：</strong><br />\nlianjie.css文件：</p>\n<pre class=\"line-numbers language-css\" data-language=\"css\"><code class=\"language-css\"><span class=\"token comment\">/* CSS Document */</span>\n<span class=\"token selector\">h3</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">&#123;</span><span class=\"token property\">font-weight</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">:</span> normal<span class=\"token punctuation\">;</span> <span class=\"token property\">background-color</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">:</span> #66CC99<span class=\"token punctuation\">;</span><span class=\"token property\">height</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">:</span> 50px<span class=\"token punctuation\">;</span> <span class=\"token property\">line-height</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">:</span> 50px<span class=\"token punctuation\">;</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">&#125;</span>\n<span class=\"token selector\">span</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">&#123;</span> <span class=\"token property\">color</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">:</span> #FF0000<span class=\"token punctuation\">;</span> <span class=\"token property\">font-weight</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">:</span> bold<span class=\"token punctuation\">;</span> <span class=\"token punctuation\">&#125;</span><span aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"line-numbers-rows\"><span></span><span></span><span></span></span></code></pre>\n<p>lianjie-2.css文件：</p>\n<pre class=\"line-numbers language-css\" data-language=\"css\"><code class=\"language-css\"><span class=\"token comment\">/* CSS Document */</span>\n<span class=\"token selector\">p</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">&#123;</span><span class=\"token property\">color</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">:</span> #FF3333<span class=\"token punctuation\">;</span> <span class=\"token property\">font-weight</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">:</span> bold<span class=\"token punctuation\">;</span> <span class=\"token property\">border-bottom</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">:</span>3px dashed #009933<span class=\"token punctuation\">;</span> <span class=\"token property\">line-height</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">:</span> 30px<span class=\"token punctuation\">;</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">&#125;</span><span aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"line-numbers-rows\"><span></span><span></span></span></code></pre>\n<p>HTML文件:</p>\n<pre class=\"line-numbers language-html\" data-language=\"html\"><code class=\"language-html\"><span class=\"token doctype\"><span class=\"token punctuation\">&lt;!</span><span class=\"token doctype-tag\">doctype</span> <span class=\"token name\">html</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">></span></span>\n<span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token punctuation\">&lt;</span>html</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">></span></span>\n\n<span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token punctuation\">&lt;</span>head</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">></span></span>\n    <span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token punctuation\">&lt;</span>meta</span> <span class=\"token attr-name\">charset</span><span class=\"token attr-value\"><span class=\"token punctuation attr-equals\">=</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">\"</span>utf-8<span class=\"token punctuation\">\"</span></span><span class=\"token punctuation\">></span></span>\n    <span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token punctuation\">&lt;</span>title</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">></span></span><span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token punctuation\">&lt;/</span>title</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">></span></span>\n    <span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token punctuation\">&lt;</span>link</span> <span class=\"token attr-name\">href</span><span class=\"token attr-value\"><span class=\"token punctuation attr-equals\">=</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">\"</span>lianjie.css<span class=\"token punctuation\">\"</span></span> <span class=\"token attr-name\">type</span><span class=\"token attr-value\"><span class=\"token punctuation attr-equals\">=</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">\"</span>text/css<span class=\"token punctuation\">\"</span></span> <span class=\"token attr-name\">rel</span><span class=\"token attr-value\"><span class=\"token punctuation attr-equals\">=</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">\"</span>stylesheet<span class=\"token punctuation\">\"</span></span> <span class=\"token punctuation\">/></span></span>\n    <span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token punctuation\">&lt;</span>link</span> <span class=\"token attr-name\">href</span><span class=\"token attr-value\"><span class=\"token punctuation attr-equals\">=</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">\"</span>lianjie-2.css<span class=\"token punctuation\">\"</span></span> <span class=\"token attr-name\">type</span><span class=\"token attr-value\"><span class=\"token punctuation attr-equals\">=</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">\"</span>text/css<span class=\"token punctuation\">\"</span></span> <span class=\"token attr-name\">rel</span><span class=\"token attr-value\"><span class=\"token punctuation attr-equals\">=</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">\"</span>stylesheet<span class=\"token punctuation\">\"</span></span> <span class=\"token punctuation\">/></span></span>\n<span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token punctuation\">&lt;/</span>head</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">></span></span>\n\n<span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token punctuation\">&lt;</span>body</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">></span></span>\n    <span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token punctuation\">&lt;</span>p</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">></span></span>我是被lianjie-2.css文件控制的，楼下的你呢？？<span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token punctuation\">&lt;/</span>p</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">></span></span>\n    <span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token punctuation\">&lt;</span>h3</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">></span></span>楼上的,<span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token punctuation\">&lt;</span>span</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">></span></span>lianjie.css<span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token punctuation\">&lt;/</span>span</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">></span></span>文件给我穿的花衣服。<span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token punctuation\">&lt;/</span>h3</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">></span></span>\n<span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token punctuation\">&lt;/</span>body</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">></span></span>\n\n<span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token punctuation\">&lt;/</span>html</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">></span></span><span aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"line-numbers-rows\"><span></span><span></span><span></span><span></span><span></span><span></span><span></span><span></span><span></span><span></span><span></span><span></span><span></span><span></span><span></span><span></span></span></code></pre>\n<p>&lt;link /&gt; 标签定义文档与外部资源的关系。常用属性有href(链接目标)、type(链接文档的类型)、rel(链接外部文件的关联类型)、title(样式表标题)。</p>\n<p>其中rel属性的属性值有alternate、author、help、icon、licence、next、pingback、prefetch、prev、search、sidebar、stylesheet、tag。</p>\n<p>链接到CSS时，type选择text/css，rel选择stylesheet。</p>\n<p>通过title属性可以做到在多种样式直接切换。</p>\n<p>title属性和rel属性存在联系，来的网页文档会使用多个&lt;link /&gt;元素导入不同的外部文件。如样式文件，脚本文件，主题文件，甚至可以包括个人自定义的其他补充文件。导入这么多不同类型、名称各异的文件后，可以使用title属性进行选择。这时，属性的作用就显现出来了。它可以指定网页文件初始显示时应用的导入文件类型。目前只能关联样式表类型。</p>\n<p>外部样式是CSS应用最佳方案，一个样式表文件可以被多个网页文件引用，同时一个网页文件可以导入多个样式表，方法是重复使用&lt;link /&gt;元素导入不同的样式表文件。</p>\n<h3 id=\"导入样式\"><a class=\"markdownIt-Anchor\" href=\"#导入样式\"></a> 导入样式</h3>\n<p>使用@import命令导入外部样式表。<br />\ndaoru.css文件：</p>\n<pre class=\"line-numbers language-css\" data-language=\"css\"><code class=\"language-css\"><span class=\"token comment\">/* CSS Document */</span>\n<span class=\"token atrule\"><span class=\"token rule\">@import</span> <span class=\"token url\"><span class=\"token function\">url</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span><span class=\"token string url\">\"lianjie-2.css\"</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span></span><span class=\"token punctuation\">;</span></span>\n<span class=\"token selector\">p</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">&#123;</span><span class=\"token property\">text-indent</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">:</span>3em<span class=\"token punctuation\">;</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">&#125;</span><span aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"line-numbers-rows\"><span></span><span></span><span></span></span></code></pre>\n<p>HTML文件：</p>\n<pre class=\"line-numbers language-html\" data-language=\"html\"><code class=\"language-html\"><span class=\"token doctype\"><span class=\"token punctuation\">&lt;!</span><span class=\"token doctype-tag\">doctype</span> <span class=\"token name\">html</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">></span></span>\n<span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token punctuation\">&lt;</span>html</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">></span></span>\n\n<span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token punctuation\">&lt;</span>head</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">></span></span>\n    <span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token punctuation\">&lt;</span>meta</span> <span class=\"token attr-name\">charset</span><span class=\"token attr-value\"><span class=\"token punctuation attr-equals\">=</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">\"</span>utf-8<span class=\"token punctuation\">\"</span></span><span class=\"token punctuation\">></span></span>\n    <span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token punctuation\">&lt;</span>title</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">></span></span><span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token punctuation\">&lt;/</span>title</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">></span></span>\n    <span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token punctuation\">&lt;</span>style</span> <span class=\"token attr-name\">type</span><span class=\"token attr-value\"><span class=\"token punctuation attr-equals\">=</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">\"</span>text/css<span class=\"token punctuation\">\"</span></span><span class=\"token punctuation\">></span></span><span class=\"token style\"><span class=\"token language-css\">\n        <span class=\"token atrule\"><span class=\"token rule\">@import</span> <span class=\"token url\"><span class=\"token function\">url</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span>lianjie.css<span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span></span><span class=\"token punctuation\">;</span></span>\n        <span class=\"token atrule\"><span class=\"token rule\">@import</span> <span class=\"token url\"><span class=\"token function\">url</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span>daoru.css<span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span></span><span class=\"token punctuation\">;</span></span>\n\n        <span class=\"token selector\">body</span> <span class=\"token punctuation\">&#123;</span>\n            <span class=\"token property\">background-color</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">:</span> #e4e929<span class=\"token punctuation\">;</span>\n        <span class=\"token punctuation\">&#125;</span>\n    </span></span><span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token punctuation\">&lt;/</span>style</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">></span></span>\n<span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token punctuation\">&lt;/</span>head</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">></span></span>\n\n<span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token punctuation\">&lt;</span>body</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">></span></span>\n    <span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token punctuation\">&lt;</span>div</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">></span></span>\n        <span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token punctuation\">&lt;</span>p</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">></span></span>我是被lianjie-2.css文件控制的，楼下的你呢？？<span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token punctuation\">&lt;/</span>p</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">></span></span>\n        <span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token punctuation\">&lt;</span>h3</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">></span></span>楼上的,<span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token punctuation\">&lt;</span>span</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">></span></span>lianjie.css<span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token punctuation\">&lt;/</span>span</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">></span></span>文件给我穿的花衣服。<span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token punctuation\">&lt;/</span>h3</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">></span></span>\n    <span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token punctuation\">&lt;/</span>div</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">></span></span>\n<span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token punctuation\">&lt;/</span>body</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">></span></span>\n\n<span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token punctuation\">&lt;/</span>html</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">></span></span><span aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"line-numbers-rows\"><span></span><span></span><span></span><span></span><span></span><span></span><span></span><span></span><span></span><span></span><span></span><span></span><span></span><span></span><span></span><span></span><span></span><span></span><span></span><span></span><span></span><span></span><span></span><span></span></span></code></pre>\n<p>注意在&lt;style&gt;中@import语句必须写标签中靠前的位置，后接CSS样式，否则可能导致样式失效。在CSS文件中使用@import也应该如此。</p>\n<p><strong>&lt;link /&gt;和@import导入样式表的区别：</strong></p>\n<blockquote><span class=\"custom-blockquote-svg\"><svg width=\"24\" height=\"24\" viewBox=\"0 0 24 24\" fill=\"\" xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/2000/svg\" data-reactroot=\"\">\n<path fill=\"\" d=\"M22 12C22 6.5 17.5 2 12 2C6.5 2 2 6.5 2 12C2 17.5 6.5 22 12 22C13.8 22 15.5 21.5 17 20.6L22 22L20.7 17C21.5 15.5 22 13.8 22 12Z\" undefined=\"1\"></path>\n<path fill=\"\" d=\"M15.97 11.5H16.04C17.12 11.5 18 12.38 18 13.47V13.53C18 14.62 17.12 15.5 16.03 15.5H15.96C14.88 15.5 14 14.62 14 13.53V13.46C14 12.38 14.88 11.5 15.97 11.5Z\" undefined=\"1\"></path>\n<path fill=\"\" d=\"M7.97 11.5H8.04C9.12 11.5 10 12.38 10 13.47V13.53C10 14.62 9.12 15.5 8.03 15.5H7.97C6.88 15.5 6 14.62 6 13.53V13.46C6 12.38 6.88 11.5 7.97 11.5Z\" undefined=\"1\"></path>\n<path stroke-linejoin=\"round\" stroke-linecap=\"round\" stroke-miterlimit=\"10\" stroke-width=\"2\" stroke=\"\" d=\"M17 8.5C15.23 8.97 14.07 10.84 14.01 13.27C14 13.33 14 13.4 14 13.47V13.5\"></path>\n<path stroke-linejoin=\"round\" stroke-linecap=\"round\" stroke-miterlimit=\"10\" stroke-width=\"2\" stroke=\"\" d=\"M9 8.5C7.23 8.97 6.07 10.84 6.01 13.27C6 13.33 6 13.4 6 13.47V13.5\"></path>\n<path stroke-linejoin=\"round\" stroke-linecap=\"round\" stroke-miterlimit=\"10\" stroke-width=\"2\" stroke=\"\" d=\"M15.97 11.5H16.04C17.12 11.5 18 12.38 18 13.47V13.53C18 14.62 17.12 15.5 16.03 15.5H15.96C14.88 15.5 14 14.62 14 13.53V13.46C14 12.38 14.88 11.5 15.97 11.5Z\"></path>\n<path stroke-linejoin=\"round\" stroke-linecap=\"round\" stroke-miterlimit=\"10\" stroke-width=\"2\" stroke=\"\" d=\"M7.97 11.5H8.04C9.12 11.5 10 12.38 10 13.47V13.53C10 14.62 9.12 15.5 8.03 15.5H7.97C6.88 15.5 6 14.62 6 13.53V13.46C6 12.38 6.88 11.5 7.97 11.5Z\"></path>\n</svg>\n</span><p>link属于HTML标签，而@import是CSS提供的。<br />\nlink和页面同时加载，@import引用的CSS会等页面被加载完再加载。<br />\nlink兼容性更好。<br />\nlink的优先级更高。</p></blockquote>\n<h2 id=\"结束\"><a class=\"markdownIt-Anchor\" href=\"#结束\"></a> 结束</h2>\n<p>学习了CSS基本语法和如何在HTML文件中使用CSS，接下来学习CSS选择器方面的知识。</p>\n","feature":true,"text":" CSS语法 CSS规则由两个主要的部分构成：选择器，以及一条或多条声明 选择器通常是您需要改变样式的对象，这些对象可以是某个标签、所有网页对象、指定Class或ID值等。 每条声明由一个属性和一个值组成。 属性是CSS提供的设置好的样式选项。每个属性有一个值。属性和值被冒号分隔...","link":"","photos":[],"count_time":{"symbolsCount":"5.7k","s